{"tid":2220969,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"༄༊࿆日研究公佈17項容易「孤獨死」的人特質，你中咗幾樣？༊࿆࿐","createTime":"2020-09-28T04:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T09:09:23.000Z","uid":38539,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7a61b6455111e1fca2a118188bebcfeab8825266","tid":2220969,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"日本是「孤獨死」大國，一年一千萬人呈孤立生活狀態，出過不少本「孤獨死」專書的作家菅野久美子，甚至將這些人形容成「孤獨死預備軍」。在「孤獨死」一族中，陷入擺爛「自我忽視」（Self-neglect）佔了八成。<br />\n<br />\n一般而言，人們有追求幸福的慾望，幸福的決定因素不是錢也不是權力，而是和他人建立信賴、親密的關係。很多研究都發現，人際關係稀薄容易造成孤獨死，進而演變成社會問題，一旦陷入自我忽視（Self-neglect），把居所變垃圾屋，一旦有這樣的意識之後，就很難救得出來。<br />\n<br />\n因為離婚、未婚或人生挫折等種種原因一個人寂寞的生活，過度的自我放縱、不注重健康、抗拒醫療、居所堆滿垃圾，甚至沉淪酒精自我麻醉，等同慢性自殺，容易陷入「孤獨死」的人通常有以下特質：<br />\n<br />\n1．作習不規律<br />\n<br />\n2．沒有男朋友或女朋友<br />\n<br />\n3．沒有工作一直待在家的人<br />\n<br />\n4．在家就可以工作的人<br />\n<br />\n5．偏食不講究健康的人<br />\n<br />\n6．與人交往嫌麻煩的人<br />\n<br />\n7．有慢性病的人<br />\n<br />\n8．本來就不喜歡人類的人<br />\n<br />\n9．連FB、推特等社交軟體都不用的人<br />\n<br />\n10．過度重視一個人就可以完成的興趣的人<br />\n<br />\n11．除工作以外就沒有朋友的人<br />\n<br />\n12．不參加任何地區或社交活動的人<br />\n<br />\n13．運動不足而且肥胖的人<br />\n<br />\n14．居家派的人<br />\n<br />\n15．租房子住的人<br />\n<br />\n16．親人都沒在身邊的人<br />\n<br />\n17．討厭和別人說話的人"},{"pid":"a79c7d3bf14adc16a566d522172a4058ff510b57","tid":2220969,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"4咪即係WFH?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa412399c2f5bd529a8c6321cd9778326f26f03","tid":2220969,"uid":127929,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"保守估計五成連登仔會中第2同14<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a93794090fe7f69e27148899abe699407345c68","tid":2220969,"uid":38539,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a79c7d3bf14adc16a566d522172a4058ff510b57","tid":2220969,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"4咪即係WFH?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"當然依家疫情例外，佢應該指一般狀況都WFH"},{"pid":"c39fa1b6f4be4e6ba4afb08a4fa9b5dd806bde49","tid":2220969,"uid":8726,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"中10樣"},{"pid":"2f0d43f4c81f835550621a0ba0dd238aa937c330","tid":2220969,"uid":178205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"2，5-14，17中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f009524e6a41860d63ca63e644778b1c9e4918ef","tid":2220969,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c39fa1b6f4be4e6ba4afb08a4fa9b5dd806bde49","tid":2220969,"uid":8726,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"中10樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:53:26.000Z","msg":"有冇中2,14<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4778d58123ef501d5e6aeb8ebfb9f0153a4f4f3c","tid":2220969,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f009524e6a41860d63ca63e644778b1c9e4918ef","tid":2220969,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c39fa1b6f4be4e6ba4afb08a4fa9b5dd806bde49","tid":2220969,"uid":8726,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"中10樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:53:26.000Z","msg":"有冇中2,14<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:54:55.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"c5cac74d5e53804e7c3366544c94d62c637ed4c3","tid":2220969,"uid":57914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c39fa1b6f4be4e6ba4afb08a4fa9b5dd806bde49","tid":2220969,"uid":8726,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"中10樣"},"citedBy":1,"re